def calculate_starting_mark(height: float) -> float:
    """
    Calculate the best starting mark for a pole vaulter based on their height.

    Parameters:
    height (float): The height of the vaulter in meters.

    Returns:
    float: The best starting mark in meters, rounded to two decimal places.
    """
    return round(9.45 - (10.67 - 9.45) / (1.83 - 1.52) * (height - 1.52), 2)
